{"tid":2493762,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"死黑警 還命！！！","createTime":"2021-04-18T07:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-18T12:19:18.000Z","uid":261505,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"514f71017dde15737b3f7ba2b7a75faf985f223f","tid":2493762,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:06:57.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】美國芝加哥一名13歲拉丁裔男童持槍逃避警方追截時，被白人警員擊斃。<br />\n當局公開事發片段，男童托萊多胸口中槍後當場昏迷。警員為他心外壓急救，並召喚救護車。其他警員陸續趕到，在現場地下找到一把手槍。<br />\n事發於上月29日凌晨，男童和另一名男子在街上被警員截查，二人逃走。警員追捕時，多次要求男童停下和舉高手。男童家人的律師指，當時男童有按警員指示，不應向他開槍。市長促請公眾冷靜，等待獨立調查完成再下判斷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母黑警又殺人<br />\n點解唔向天嗚槍示警？<br />\n點解唔射手指甲？"},{"pid":"c9ddecb9851f9eb121a22581f78e6227f075f6f2","tid":2493762,"uid":48083,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-18T07:08:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcxQdFPN8WJ5wjKZnQiTM3uQZF5Pmx8H22pmuDqcuYY5j?filename=iXpqfu7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiXpqfu7.png&h=ab028cbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人睇完緬甸開槍覺得香港警察真係好仁慈？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2409031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2409031</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n講能到郵寄選票一定成箱Biden假票咁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2270992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2270992</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n熱烈祝賀屯門瓏門冰室執笠<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2326986\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2326986</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://filedn.eu/l9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfUaJ/LIHKG_on99/on9_son_2021/261505/261505.3_.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffiledn.eu%2Fl9Hq1YKLkJ4m0VSXcdcfU